<p>MOX fuel irradiated in a <a href="./Fast_reactor" title="Fast reactor">fast reactor</a> (average of 5 samples with burnup 66 to 120GWd/t) <a href="http://wwwsoc.nii.ac.jp/aesj/publication/JNST2001/No.10/38_912-914.pdf" class="external autonumber" title="http://wwwsoc.nii.ac.jp/aesj/publication/JNST2001/No.10/38_912-914.pdf" rel="nofollow">[1]</a> contained 3.09×10<sup>-3</sup>% curium with isotopic content:</p>
<table class="wikitable" align="right">
<tr>
