<p>The proportions of the three most common curium isotopes in 53 MWd/kg <a href="./LEU" title="LEU">LEU</a> spent fuel 20 years after discharge were reported in <a href="http://www.princeton.edu/~globsec/publications/pdf/13_3%20Kang%20vonhippel.pdf" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.princeton.edu/~globsec/publications/pdf/13_3%20Kang%20vonhippel.pdf" rel="nofollow">[2]</a> (page 4) as:</p>
